wiki.content: This track is the 3rd single from Madonna's latest album MDNA. "Turn Up the Radio" went to #1 on the U.S. Billboard Hot Dance Club Play Chart in the Summer of 2012. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
wiki.summary: This track is the 3rd single from Madonna's latest album MDNA. "Turn Up the Radio" went to #1 on the U.S. Billboard Hot Dance Club Play Chart in the Summer of 2012.
